Title: Graphite metrics: Introduced rule to configure host metrics sent to Graphite
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: cmc
Date: 1681395873
Edition: cee
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0p27

The new rule <tt>Send host metrics to Graphite</tt> allows you to configure which host metrics are sent to graphite.
Previous versions always sent the <tt>VALUE</tt> to graphite, with no way to disable the metrics altogether.
Now you can configure a rule and turn everything off.
